    "description": "《Looking for Aliens》（寻找外星人）是一款隐藏物品游戏，让你通过外星人的新闻节目来看世界。在25个充满活力和细节的地点猎取物品，包括51区、梦幻世界和外太空！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/43e11b13a491b0f83977f272ff63591a.poster.avif?t=1711088535\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/43e11b13a491b0f83977f272ff63591a.webm?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/43e11b13a491b0f83977f272ff63591a.mp4?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>认识迷人的银河系电视主持人和一个叫扎恩的地球人。哎呀，应该是肖恩！找到任何能帮助肖恩证明外星生命存在并返回地球的物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/37ac252b3f7814651135e3c93781fcb4.poster.avif?t=1711088535\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/37ac252b3f7814651135e3c93781fcb4.webm?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/37ac252b3f7814651135e3c93781fcb4.mp4?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>从外星人的眼中，人类看起来像什么？到底是谁登陆了月球？宇宙飞船藏在哪里？银河系中最危险的东西是什么？答案就在《Looking for Aliens》！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/783147585a80a640038d0787795cbeab.poster.avif?t=1711088535\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/783147585a80a640038d0787795cbeab.webm?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/783147585a80a640038d0787795cbeab.mp4?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在25个彩色关卡中找到250多个隐藏物品<br></li><li>跟随地球人肖恩的冒险之旅，他努力证明外星人的存在<br></li><li>享受基于有趣文本提示的隐藏对象机制<br></li><li>探索一个高度互动的环境 - 关闭隐身全息图，瞥见人物的梦境，或者干脆吃光所有的食物！<br></li><li>请勿让眼睛疲劳过度 - 你可以放大所有的位置<br></li><li>在地球上度过了艰难的一天之后，休息一下，享受轻松的幽默、音乐和流行文化</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/4cb5115c165809010689ac5103da4cc6.poster.avif?t=1711088535\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/4cb5115c165809010689ac5103da4cc6.webm?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733500/extras/4cb5115c165809010689ac5103da4cc6.mp4?t=1711088535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
